589
01:20:38,698 --> 01:20:40,012
¿Esther?

590
01:20:40,719 --> 01:20:42,173
¡Esther!

591
01:20:46,466 --> 01:20:49,429
Mi ojo...

592
01:20:54,784 --> 01:20:56,939
Era una presencia demoníaca.

593
01:20:57,061 --> 01:20:59,732
Y estaba usando a nuestra
Annabelle para manipularnos...

594
01:20:59,767 --> 01:21:02,339
