No.

655
01:28:21,553 --> 01:28:23,152
No, no.

656
01:29:10,812 --> 01:29:12,224
¡No!

657
01:29:42,803 --> 01:29:45,724
Señor, ayúdame.
Señor, ayuda.

658
01:29:45,765 --> 01:29:47,454
Ayuda...

659
01:29:48,434 --> 01:29:49,892
Carol, soy yo.

660
01:29:49,936 --> 01:29:51,465
Soy yo.

661
01:29:51,651 --> 01:29:53,630
Ven.
Vamos.

662
01:29:53,745 --> 01:29:55,145
¡Ay, Dios!

663
01:32:05,031 --> 01:32:06,543
No.

664
