01:36:08,316 --> 01:36:09,591
¡No!

680
01:36:11,262 --> 01:36:12,706
<i>¡Déjame salir!</i>

681
01:36:12,966 --> 01:36:14,640
<i>¡Déjame salir!</i>

682
01:36:15,118 --> 01:36:17,287
