683
01:36:50,046 --> 01:36:51,428
¡Vamos!

684
01:36:52,181 --> 01:36:53,608
¡Corre!

685
01:36:58,628 --> 01:36:59,941
¡Vamos!

686
01:37:08,896 --> 01:37:11,403
- ¡Hermana Charlotte!
- ¡Hermana Charlotte!

687
01:38:50,282 --> 01:38:51,717
¿Hay algo?

688
01:38:52,192 --> 01:38:53,831
Me temo que no.

689
01:38:54,321 --> 01:38:56,073
